89 water shall have been used or consumed directly in or for the
90 production, generation, processing, storage, delivery, or
91 transmission of electricity, natural gas, or domestic water;
92 (5) Whenever electricity purchased for storage, use, or
93 other consumption is used or consumed by a manufacturer or
94 compounder in an electrolytic or electrothermal manufacturing
